==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interminate
<hw>In*ter"mi*nate</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>interminatus</ets>;
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>terminatus</ets>, p. p. of terminate.]</ety>
<def>Endless; <as>as, <ex>interminate</ex> sleep</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Chapman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
