==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Interminate
<hw>In*ter"mi*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>interminatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>interminari</ets>;
<ets>inter</ets> between + <ets>minari</ets> to threaten.]</ety> <def>To
menace; to threaten.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bp.
Hall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

